description:
This is the additional puzzle pack for "Jigsaw Masterpieces". The following 10 puzzle images are included.
-Beautiful park on Madre Island, Italy
-Kyoto in autumn
-Park filled with hydrangeas
-Japanese Garden with Waterfall
-Gardens of Vancouver Island
-Colorful tulips in the park
-Arch of Roses
-Antique Fountain
-Colorful Japanese-style garden
-Wooden swing surrounded by flowers
name: Colorful Garden
